These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, fanta, water, almond-milk, coffee
The people have 5 different jobs:  lawyer, electrician, engineer, musician, manager
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, folk, disco, metal
There are 5 different nationalities: russian, chinese, italian, mexican, argentine
 1. the italian is on the left or right of the manager##3
 2. the lawyer is in an odd position##4
 3. the fan of jazz is on the left of the chinese##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
 6. the fan of disco is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the manager is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 8. the argentine is in an even position##4
 9. the russian is on the left or right of the musician##3
10. the fan of folk is the engineer##1
11. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
13. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the chinese##1
14. the argentine is on the left of the fan of metal##1
15. the fan of disco is the person drinking almond-milk##1
16. the fan of disco is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |        2        |     3      |    4     |     5     |
| Beverage      | water    | lemonade   | almond-milk     | coffee      | fanta      |
| Job           | engineer | manager | lawyer    | musician | electrician |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | jazz         | disco      | r&b      | metal    |
| Nationality   | italian    | mexican         | chinese | argentine  | russian   |

