.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, rock-climbing, gardening, baking, singing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: metal, indie, punk, house, r&b
5 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, ferret, frog, goat
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, van, subway, tram, scooter
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the fan of r&b##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 6. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person driving the motorbike##2
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
10. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
11. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
13. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
14. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | baking | rock-climbing | gardening   | dancing | singing |
| Music-Genre   | punk      | indie   | r&b    | metal        | house        |
| Pet           | frog         | goat  | hamster  | guinea-pig   | ferret      |
| Transport     | motorbike        | tram  | subway | scooter | van         |

