.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, almond-milk, water, 7up
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, superhero, romance, zombie
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, biathlon, skiing, sailing, handball
The people use 5 different means of transport: quad-bike, boat, helicopter, roller, jet-ski
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the person drinking water is the person drinking water##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 9. the person watching romance movies is the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person driving the roller is the person drinking 7up##1
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person driving the boat and the person watching animation movies##2
13. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
14. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
16. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |      4       |       5       |
| Beverage      | 7up       | iced-tea   | sprite    | water     | almond-milk |
| Movie-Genre   | animation     | documentary   | superhero   | romance | zombie       |
| Sport         | handball | biathlon | surfing | sailing     | skiing        |
| Transport     | roller       | quad-bike     | boat  | helicopter   | jet-ski         |

