 2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
 3. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 4. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
 5. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 6. the person driving the airplane is the person eating cauliflower##1
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 9. the person eating apricot is the fan of dubstep##1
10. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
11. the fan of blues is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
14. the person eating cauliflower is the person eating cauliflower##1
15. the person driving the tram is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
16. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
17. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3

