 4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the mexican is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the thai##3
 8. the owner of the rat is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person eating radish##2
 9. the polish is on the right of the nigerian##1
10. the polish is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
11. the polish is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
13. the person eating peach is on the far right##1
14. the person eating radish is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Food          | radish      | lemon       | raspberry | grapefruit | peach |
| Nationality   | thai       | colombian    | mexican  | nigerian  | polish |
| Pet           | dog         | rat | pony      | frog     | turtle    |
| Sport         | badminton | swimming   | climbing   | soccer  | skiing |

